Ando forovipen (politika) yek '''sherutno foro''' si o [[foro]] kay beshel o [[xulyaripen]] le [[them]]esko vay yek kotor themesko.

Butvar o sherutno foro si vi o bareder, o may importanto foro thanesko. Shay te avel o mashkar katar shirdyas (astardyas) te kideren sa le riga kothar ando yek phandlo them. Si sherutne forurya kerdine te aven numa yek xulayaripenasko than dur katar e importante forurya le themeske, sar [[Canberra|Kênberra]] andar [[Australiya|Avstraliya]] vay [[Ottawa|Ottava]] andar [[Kanada|Kanâdo]]

== Thema le buteder sherutne forurenca ==
{{dikhvi|Patrinipen le themengo le buteder sherutne forurenca}}

Si thema so len si len buteder sherutne forurya. Sar misalyake, andi [[Afrika le Sudosko]] o administratikano sherutno foro si kai [[Pretoriya]] o foro le zakonurengo kai [[Cape Town]] thai le krisako foro kai [[Bloemfontein]].

== Le bareder sherutne forurya ==
[[Chitro:Capital not largest city.PNG|thumb|Thema kay o sherutno foro nay o bareder foro]]
Butvar yek sherutno foro nay o bareder foro le themesko. Le bareder sherutne forurya ando fishtesavo [[Barodvip]] si:

* [[Afrika]]: [[Kayro]] (11,146,000)
* [[Asiya]]: [[Tokyo]] (35,237,000)
* [[Europa|Evropa]]: [[Moskova]] (13,600,000)
* [[Nordutni Amerika]]: [[Mexiko (foro)]] (17,809,471)
* [[Okeyaniya]]: [[Wellington]] (445,400)
* [[Sudutni Amerika]]: [[Buenos Ayres]] (14,230,000)

